name: XTK Shaker Bottle Protein Shaker Bottles with Storage and Mix Ball, 16OZ Sports Water Bottle with Pill Organizer,Leak Proof Portable Shaker Bottles for Protein Mixes and Pre Work Out,BPA Free(purple)
description:
Our shaker cup combines multiple functions in one, allowing you to store protein powder and pills. The included metal wire mixer can also smoothly blend your drink, making it very practical and convenient. It is the best choice for sports enthusiasts to supplement nutrition and hydration, and it has the following features:
1. Made of food-grade material, non-toxic and BPA-free.
2. With a capacity of 16OZ, equipped with storage compartments for protein powder and pills.
3. Easy to clean and dishwasher safe.
4. Very portable and suitable for on-the-go use.
5. Available in a variety of rich colors.
6. Worry-free after-sales service.
7.Package includes: 1 shaker bottle, 1 shaker balls, perfect for mixing protein shakes, smoothies, and supplements.
The shaker bottle is designed to be made from premium food grade, high quality BPA-free plastic. Not easily broken, is completely safe to store your drink in protein shaker bottle. Screw caps and safety clamps ensure overall smoothie cup tightness, prevent messy spills, and maximize the cleanliness of your car and bag even when you are in a hurry in the morning. Press the safety flap and hear a click to confirm that the lid is tight, so you can take it outside or exercise with you.
Our shaker bottles for protein mixes feature multiple features such as leak proof seal, wide spout with tight lid, hiking buckle carrying handle.
The gym bottle comes with a coil spring mixer for the protein mix, which mixes the protein shake faster than the stir ball so it doesn't clump when shaken, and the shake ball hits the bottom so there's no more residue on the bottom, stirring more evenly.

name: SHAKESPHERE Tumbler: Protein Shaker Bottle and Smoothie Cup, 24 oz - Bladeless Blender Cup Purees Raw Fruit with No Blending Ball - Drink Powder Mix Shake Mixer for Pre Workout, Gym (Matte Black)
description:
Easy Shake Mixing In a Premium Tumbler

ShakeSphere Tumbler is an ingeniously designed shaker bottle with patented capsule shape. Its innovative shape allows for superior mixing of supplements, vitamins, powders, drinks, fruits, while enabling super-fast cleanup!

All this is enhanced by an easy to clean, highly durable and resistant rugged design. A gorgeous sleek look rounds out the package.

Where impeccable quality mix with flawless practicality

Perfect Blending Ratios

Available with a 24.6 FL OZ capacity, ShakeSphere is the best protein shaker after your workout, lifting session, swimming, running, weightlifting and any other sport. Its unique design also makes it easy to carry around.

Perfect Drinking Control

The finger loop and the slide cap with silicone making carrying and drinking from the ShakeSphere Tumbler a joy. The hemisphere base & lid keep shaker standing when you need it. Excellent for any sport and fitness enthusiast.

Striking Rugged Build

The ShakeSphere Tumbler is food safe, CE certified and BPA free. It is designed to be the most convenient, functional and hygienic shaker bottle on the market.

features: AWARD WINNING DESIGN - Voted Best Protein Shaker bottle by Men's Health and others! ShakeSphere's advanced hybrid blender bottle smoothie cup mixes various ingredients to drinkable perfection in the patented capsule shape, without needing a blender ball or mesh grid.

ZERO CLUMPS OR STUCK POWDERS - #NoCorners lifestyle. Perfect as a gym bottle shaker cup or pre workout bottle. Centrifugal force breaks down powder supplements in a mere 5 seconds of quick shaking. With no corners, nothing gets left behind after you’re done.

BLENDS FRUIT WITH NO BLADES - Shake for another 5 seconds and you can even enjoy soft fruit in your shake for the ultimate post-workout recovery boost! (Remember: it's a bladeless bottle blender, not a magic miracle device. Fruit must first be soft, ripe, and cut into small pieces)

EFFORTLESS CLEANING, NO ODOR - Tacti-cool and modern. Anti-gag reflex, no-odor, smell-proof design is freezer safe. NOT dishwasher safe. But that doesn't matter. Because all it takes is 5 seconds of rapid rinsing with cold water, and you're ready for your next shake.

THE WORLD’S #1 SHAKER. PERIOD. Voted Best Splurge product by Shape.com for a reason! name: VOLTRX shaker Bottle, Gallium USB C Rechargeable Electric protein shake Mixer, Cups for protein and Meal Replacement shakes, BPA Free, Made with Tritan, 24oz
description:
Innovative Design All Over

VOLTRX, a magical new way to mix and the ultimate solution to eliminate clumping. New and improved, VOLTRX Gallium electric shaker bottle benefits from patented technology to enhance its power and endurance. The innovative design allows you to clean every corner of the protein mixer cup whilst the tight-fitting screw-on cap ensures it stays watertight. Made with US Tritan material, our electric shaker cup are BPA-Free with an IPX5 waterproof base. VOLTRX is better than ever.

Mix Like A Pro; Stirred Not Shaken

The new patented technologies that built VOLTRX Gallium electric protein shaker bottle provide the ultimate solution to eliminate caking. Traditional shaker bottles with wire mixing balls are hard to clean, noisy and leave lumps of powder in your drink. And all the ballless protein shakers are even worse. Smooth shakes are mixed, not shaken, and the VOLTRX protein shake mixer takes mixing to a whole new level.

Dissolve Within 15s

6000rpm powerful motor with a unique patented blade design and ingenious transmission construction of VOLTRX Gallium electric shaker bottle ensures that protein powder will completely dissolve in liquid within 15 seconds so you can enjoy that silky texture you’ve been waiting for.

Banana Can Be Added

Thanks to VOLTRX Gallium’s unparalleled power, you can now add soft mashed bananas or your favourite soft fruit puree to your protein drinks to make a delicious flavoured supplement drink.

Seamless Watertight Fit

VOLTRX Gallium protein shake mixer bottle is built to ensure a leak-proof design featuring a reliable screw cap lid and temperature-resistant material to prevent deformation. Keep the electric mixer cup closed at all times, and place it in your gym bag with confidence.

Just The Right Size

The 24oz (700ml) capacity means you can fit 16oz (480ml) of liquid with up to 3 scoops of protein powder, making VOLTRX's Gallium vortex shaker bottle an excellent size for making shakes for anyone. Even if you have big goals, VOLTRX can help you meet them.

There’s Power In Silence

Clanging ball shakers and loud blenders, step aside. Thanks to VOLTRX's patented silent motor technology, Gallium vortex protein shaker is ideal for use every morning or in the office without disturbing your family or colleagues.

Larger Handle

VOLTRX cares about every design detail which is why you can now carry the Gallium electric protein shake mixer with two fingers, plus the extended handle allows you to hang it wherever you want.

Easy To Maintain

With the IPX5 waterproof base, you can rinse your cup directly under a tap while it's on after use. Gallium self stirring protein shaker waterproof sealing rings are removable, making cleaning every part of the cup easy. It can be washed in the dishwasher after removing the motorized base.

1 Charge For 2 Months

VOLTRX is highly efficient, our designers ensured Gallium rechargeable protein shaker delivers superb power and long-lasting battery life without compromise. Just one charge is required in order to complete two months of mixing.

Designed With The Earth In Mind

VOLTRX Gallium protein shake mixer cup is designed to take care of you and Planet Earth. Our shaker bottles for protein mixes use high quality materials and responsible packaging. Made with Tritan material from the USA, they're more transparent and less fragile for long lasting quality.

Battery life 80 times 80 times 120 times

Max. water level at mixing 16oz (450ml) 16oz (450ml) 16oz (450ml)

name: FANS-ONE Electric Protein Shaker Bottle, 24oz Blender Bottles for Protein Mixes, USB C Rechargeable Shaker Cup, Made with Tritan, BPA Free Shakers for Protein Shakes, Onyx Black
description:
FANS-ONE Electric Shaker Bottle aims to take your shake-making experience to the next level.

One Button To Start, Two Operation Modes

5500rpm powerful motor and unique blade design ensure that the protein powder is completely dissolved in liquid within 30 seconds, so you can enjoy that silky texture you’ve been waiting for.

Intelligent Motor With Cool Lights

Create a pleasant and eye-catching visual effect
Long press and charge will prompt the battery level
Lights turn off intelligently when fully charged
Safety design - unable to stir during charging

Made With Premium Tritan

100% BPA Free
Made with premium Tritan, our protein shaker bottle can withstand high temperatures ≥ 100 ℃, while the others fake Tritan cups will soften when filled with ＞80℃ water

Pop-Up Lockable Lid

Easy to operate, one-click open by one hand
Leak proof design, toss it into the gym bag without worrying about spills or messes

Suitable For Multiple Raw Materials

Perfect for mixing protein powder and supplements
Please DO NOT add ice or fruit when stirring
18 ounces liquid may be the sweet spot if you pour in powder to mix

Please note that the motor base is packaged in the cup.

Q: Can the blender bottle stir fruits and ice cubes?

A: No! It is suitable for various powdered beverages.

Q: Is there a recommended mixing ratio for protein powder and liquid?

A: Recommend to add up to 16oz (450ml) of liquid, and 3 scoops (80g) of protein powder.

Q: Why can't it be stirred during charging?

A: The base has a safety design that prevents stirring during charging.

Q: Why does the base not light up?

A:Situation 1: The base is completely without power and needs to be charged for a while before being restored;

Situation 2: When the charging cable is connected and fully charged, the light will automatically turn off.

features: AWARD WINNING DESIGN - Voted Best Protein Shaker bottle by Men's Health and others! ShakeSphere's advanced hybrid blender bottle smoothie cup mixes various ingredients to drinkable perfection in the patented capsule shape, without needing a blender ball or mesh grid.

ZERO CLUMPS OR STUCK POWDERS - #NoCorners lifestyle. Perfect as a gym bottle shaker cup or pre workout bottle. Centrifugal force breaks down powder supplements in a mere 5 seconds of quick shaking. With no corners, nothing gets left behind after you’re done.

BLENDS FRUIT WITH NO BLADES - Shake for another 5 seconds and you can even enjoy soft fruit in your shake for the ultimate post-workout recovery boost! (Remember: it's a bladeless bottle blender, not a magic miracle device. Fruit must first be soft, ripe, and cut into small pieces)

EFFORTLESS CLEANING, NO ODOR - Tacti-cool and modern. Anti-gag reflex, no-odor, smell-proof design is freezer safe. NOT dishwasher safe. But that doesn't matter. Because all it takes is 5 seconds of rapid rinsing with cold water, and you're ready for your next shake.

THE WORLD’S #1 SHAKER. PERIOD. Voted Best Splurge product by Shape.com for a reason! ShakeSphere has continually evolved and continues to innovate and improve, integrating feedback over the years from athletes, fitness enthusiasts, bodybuilders, and coaches to produce the World’s #1 Shaker. Period.

name: ShakeSphere Tumbler VIEW: Protein Shaker Bottle Smoothie Cup with Clear Window, 24 oz - Bladeless Blender Cup Purees Fruit, No Mixing Ball - Drink Powder Shake Mixer for Pre Workout, Gym- Flex Wheeler Special Edition
description:
Shaksphere presents: THE TUMBLER VIEW - an upgrade to the Tumbler Original

CLEAR VIEWING WINDOW

You spoke. We listened. Now you can enjoy visible and accurate measuring of your drink and ingredients via a see-through viewing window located on the side of the tumbler. No guesswork. Even better for meal planning, macro counting, and diet restrictions.

Offering the same award-winning benefits as our original shaker, the Tumbler View features a see-through viewing window which accurately shows the measurements of your drink in both milliliters and fl oz.

FEATURES & BENEFITS:

Dimensions: 9.45 x 4.5 x 4.5 inches
24.6 fl oz
Clear Viewing Window
Measurements in mL and fl oz
BPA Free
Flat Base
Adjustable Finger Loop
Leakproof Silicone Slide Cap
Unique Capsule Shape
No Mixing Ball Needed
Easy to Clean
NOT Dishwasher Safe

BLADE-FREE BLENDING OF FRUIT AND MORE

Shake for another five seconds and you can also enjoy soft fruit in your shake for the ultimate post-workout boost! Use it to puree bananas, berries, kiwi, peaches, and other soft, ripe fruits. (But we aren’t magicians. Just seriously serious about high-performance shaker bottles. Any fruit you decide to puree must be SOFT, RIPE, and PRE-CUT into small pieces). You can even use your ShakeSphere for yogurt or for mixing ingredients in your cooking and marinade recipes

THE LAST SHAKER BOTTLE YOU’LL EVER SHAKE

Get ready to send your old shaker bottles to the recycling center! Instead of using mixing accessories like a wire ball or mesh grid, the ShakeSphere uses the centrifugal force generated by a round, no-corners design to break down powder supplements in a mere five seconds of shaking. Perfect for pre workout blends and post-workout recovery shakes. Cleaning is effortless. No brush, scrubber, or soaking needed. Rinses without a trace.

description:
About this item

STAY HYDRATED ON THE GO: Sip down your muscle building fuel during the exhaustive fitness sessions. Our shaker bottle can be used to store your pre workout drinks, post workout drinks, meal replacements or any drink you want. Perfect for carrying drinks to your fitness training, dance sessions, office, and competitions.
GET SMOOTH, DELICIOUS SHAKES ALL THE TIME: Hate lumpy shakes? The functional whisk ball that comes with the shaker bottle whips the liquid and cuts through powders, allowing you to make protein shakes on your way to the gym. No need to carry multiple accessories.

HOOK FOR EASY CARRYING- These protein drink shaker bottles come with a sturdy loop top so that you can carry it easily and hook somewhere for storage. Additionally, the bottle fits in most bottle holders so that you can always have it on your person no matter where you go.
IDEAL FOR FITNESS ENTHUSIASTS- These protein powder shaker bottles are perfect for any fitness enthusiasts or gym rats who are in constantly need of adequate nutrition. Gift it to the athlete in your life and you can bet that these bottles will see a lot of action!

description:

MAKE THE PERFECT SHAKE, EVERY TIME: Our mixing ball technology (included in each shaker) makes blending a breeze. Simply add your favorite protein powder, or supplement to your liquid, and give it a few shakes. Even the thickest powders will blend smoothly, and evenly. Say goodbye to chalky texture for good.

name: JoyJolt Triple Insulated Cocktail/Protein Shaker Bottle. 20oz Shaker Cup with Alcohol Measure Lid and Jigger Cap. 12hr Ice Cold Shaker Bottles for Protein Mixes, Shake or Smoothie Cups, Metal Mixer
description:
About this item

COLDER COCKTAILS AND SHAKES: With a JoyJolt Triple Insulated Cobbler Shaker, drinks stay cold for longer - 12 hours in fact! Our vacuum insulation is already brag worthy for its 12 hour abilities, but we also infused it with copper so you get the coldest drink even when it’s been in your hot hands or locker.
WITH TWO MEASURING LIDS! This drink mixer can be used for anything! With a 7oz Measuring Lid and 1oz Jigger Cap it’s the perfect margarita or martini shaker or shot shaker. But with its screw lid it’s also a great espresso shaker, iced coffee shaker, or even a salad dressing shaker if you so desire!
FITS YOUR CUP HOLDER, TOO! This 20 ounce ice shaker is 2.6” wide at the base and 3.5” at the top. Of course, you won’t be taking your liquor shaker on the road with booze in, but it’s handy for your pre workout cup shaker instead of in your bag. Or, smoothie cup, shakes and iced coffee!
UNIQUELY SPILL PROOF! A standard bar shaker has a press lid, but this stainless steel shaker bottle for drinks has both a screw-top lid and screw-top cap. It won’t fly off during an epic flair, and it also means you CAN stash your cocktail / protein powder shaker bottle in your bag without spills.
CORROSION RESISTANT AND BPA FREE: Your metal shaker bottle is naturally free from lead, BPA and Phthalates. And the 18/8 stainless steel construction has been infused with chromium and nickel – both food safe metals that stop our shakers going rusty! Handwash only to protect vacuum seal.
THE SHAKER OF THE YEAR! This powder coated bar shaker comes in many matte hues incl. black, white and the on-trend Veri Peri Purple - Pantone Color of The Year! Each alcohol shaker comes safely nestled in a gift box with a 12 Month Guarantee for some satisfying unboxing. Grab yours now, from JoyJolt.

name: FANS-ONE Electric Protein Shaker Bottle, 24oz Blender Bottles for Protein Mixes, USB C Rechargeable Shaker Cup, Made with Tritan, BPA Free Shakers for Protein Shakes, Onyx Black
description:
FANS-ONE Electric Shaker Bottle aims to take your shake-making experience to the next level.

One Button To Start, Two Operation Modes

5500rpm powerful motor and unique blade design ensure that the protein powder is completely dissolved in liquid within 30 seconds, so you can enjoy that silky texture you’ve been waiting for.

Intelligent Motor With Cool Lights

Create a pleasant and eye-catching visual effect
Long press and charge will prompt the battery level
Lights turn off intelligently when fully charged
Safety design - unable to stir during charging

Made With Premium Tritan

100% BPA Free
Made with premium Tritan, our protein shaker bottle can withstand high temperatures ≥ 100 ℃, while the others fake Tritan cups will soften when filled with ＞80℃ water

Pop-Up Lockable Lid

Easy to operate, one-click open by one hand
Leak proof design, toss it into the gym bag without worrying about spills or messes

Suitable For Multiple Raw Materials

Perfect for mixing protein powder and supplements
Please DO NOT add ice or fruit when stirring
18 ounces liquid may be the sweet spot if you pour in powder to mix

Please note that the motor base is packaged in the cup.

Q: Can the blender bottle stir fruits and ice cubes?

A: No! It is suitable for various powdered beverages.

Q: Is there a recommended mixing ratio for protein powder and liquid?

A: Recommend to add up to 16oz (450ml) of liquid, and 3 scoops (80g) of protein powder.

Q: Why can't it be stirred during charging?

A: The base has a safety design that prevents stirring during charging.

Q: Why does the base not light up?

A:Situation 1: The base is completely without power and needs to be charged for a while before being restored;

Situation 2: When the charging cable is connected and fully charged, the light will automatically turn off.

description:
About this item

24OZ STAINLESS STEEL SHAKER CUP: Our refillable, reusable, 24oz capacity stainless steel shaker cup is perfect for protein shakes, pre-workout drinks, iced coffee, or any beverage you want to take on the go!
TWO LID OPTIONS: Comes with 2 leak-proof lid options - the PRO lid features a flip-top cap and carry loop, while the Tumbler Lid With Straw is perfect for hot beverages and features a silicone rubber seal and smooth straw insertion.
MINDFUL DESIGN: Features triple layer vacuum insulation plus an inner copper layer to keep your drinks cold or hot for hours. It is also cup-holder compatible with a silicone base and BPA free.
SMOOTH BLENDING: The included grate allows for easy, smooth mixing of supplement powders and can also be used to hold down ice and fruit for infused drinks.
CARE INSTRUCTIONS: Wash before first use. The dual function spout is dishwasher safe, however the glass bottle is hand wash only. Soak overnight or use a soft sponge or brush to clean tough stains. Rinse well after each wash.

name: XTKS Shaker Bottle 18OZ Protein Shaker Bottles with Powder Storage & Pill Case 500ML GYM Shaker Cup for Protein Mixes with Blending Ball Leak Proof Mixer Bottle for Pre Workout,BPA Free(black)
description:
XTKS ALL-IN-ONE PROTEIN SHAKER BOTTLE

The XTKS All-in-One Protein Shaker Cup is a versatile and practical tool for fitness enthusiasts. It includes various accessories such as a mixing ball, handle, protein powder storage, and pill tray, catering to all the needs of sports enthusiasts. Its purpose is to simplify and enhance your workout routine.

Our shaker cup is a versatile all-in-one tool that allows you to store protein powder and pills.The inner wall of the shake cup features a unique curved design helps to smoothly blend your drink with mixing ball . It is the ideal choice for sports enthusiasts looking to supplement their nutrition and hydration.

Staying Hydrated And Enjoying Your Favorite Drinks On The Go

Convenient grip

The size of this GYM shaker cup is perfect, offering convenient handling and a comfortable grip. It is securely designed for easy portability and can be attached to different surfaces or equipment for added flexibility.

Built-in handle

These shaker bottles are equipped with a built-in handle on the lid ，This handle allows for easy carrying and transport, whether you're going to the gym, office, or traveling. You can conveniently hang the bottle on your finger ，ensuring quick and effortless access to your favorite beverage.

Carabiner Clip

This shaker bottle come with a carabiner clip, which is a handy attachment for outdoor enthusiasts or those on the go. The carabiner clip allows you to easily clip the bottle onto your backpack, belt loop, or gym bag, keeping it readily accessible wherever you go. This feature is particularly beneficial during activities like hiking, camping, or cycling, as it ensures you have your hydration or protein source within reach at all times.

By utilizing the internal capsule-shaped structure and the mixing ball, the shaker bottle ensures that your protein shakes, pre-workouts, or other beverages are properly mixed, without any clumps or residue. This promotes an enjoyable drinking experience, where you can confidently consume your favorite blends, knowing they are well-mixed and ready to fuel your body effectively.

Capsule-Shaped Structure: The internal capsule-shaped structure of this shaker bottle is designed to enhance the mixing process of your beverages. It helps create a vortex-like effect when you shake the bottle, ensuring that your protein powders, supplements, or other ingredients mix thoroughly and evenly. This structure helps eliminate any clumps or lumps, resulting in a smooth and consistent drink texture.
Mixing Ball: The stainless steel mixing ball is an essential component of shaker bottle. When placed inside the bottle along with your ingredients and liquid, the ball moves freely during shaking. Its purpose is to break down any powders, mix the ingredients together, and create a homogenous blend. The ball's movement assists in achieving a well-mixed drink with a smooth consistency and uniform taste.

Leak-proof

Our shaker bottle is specifically engineered to prevent leaks and spills, ensuring that your liquids stay contained within the bottle.With a leak-proof shaker bottle, you can confidently carry your drinks, whether it's water, protein shakes, or other beverages, without worrying about messy accidents.

Dual measurement markings

Our shaker bottle features dual measurement markings with milliliters (ml) and ounces (oz). These markings are conveniently etched on the side of the bottle, allowing for accurate and precise measurement of your ingredients. Whether you're following a recipe or monitoring your intake of liquids, these markings provide the necessary guidance. This feature is particularly useful for athletes, fitness enthusiasts, and individuals who want to ensure consistent and accurate measurements for their protein shakes, smoothies, or other beverages.

Durable

These shaker bottles are made from high-quality, sturdy materials , the durability ensures that the bottle can withstand regular use, whether it's being thrown into a gym bag, washed in a dishwasher, or even dropped accidentally. This durable shaker bottle is a long-lasting investment that can accompany you through countless workouts and outdoor activities.

Our Protein Shaker Bottle Is Incredibly User-friendly, With Easy Installation And Disassembly Of All Its Components

The convenience of our shaker bottle lies in its simple and intuitive design. The various parts, such as the lid, cap, and mixing ball, protein storage,pill case can be effortlessly attached or detached, allowing for quick and hassle-free assembly. Whether you want to add protein powder, mix in supplements, or simply enjoy a refreshing beverage, the versatility of our shaker bottle enables you to adapt it to your preferences.

Furthermore, the easy-to-install and detachable components of our shaker bottle make cleaning a breeze. You can disassemble the bottle effortlessly, allowing for thorough cleaning of all the nooks and crannies. This not only ensures hygiene but also prolongs the lifespan of the bottle.

name: Evolve Plant Based Protein Shake, Double Chocolate, 20g Vegan Protein, Dairy Free, No Artificial Sweeteners, Non-GMO, 10g Fiber, 11 Fl Oz (Pack of 12) - (Formula May Vary)
description:
Evolve brand. Good. Simple. Protein.

Evolve Protein Shakes are a real, vegetable-based and plant powered protein source that provides 20g of protein for sustained energy to help support your active lifestyle. Evolve Protein Shakes are made with only the highest-quality, North American grown, inherently Non-GMO pea protein. Peas are used as a companion rotational crop, a practice that returns much-needed nitrogen back to the soil. Now that's something we can all feel good about.

Evolve Protein Shakes are:

Gluten free, soy free and dairy free.

Highly nutritious and environmentally delicious.

Made with only 9-10 essential ingredients.

Non-GMO and free of artificial flavors.

An excellent source of non-GMO pre-biotic fiber which supports digestive health.

Low in fat and an excellent source of plant based protein, calcium and a good source of iron.

SUPER-POWERED SHAKE BOTTLE - The mountop shakers for protein shakes is fitted with a more powerful motor drive, with a speed of up to 7,850 rpm and a constant voltage design, you don't have to worry about low power causing the speed to drop. description:
Often imitated but never surpassed

Need a premium shaker bottle?
Tired of nasty clumps in your shaker bottles for protein mixes?
Irritated by loud and noisy protein shakers?
Lost for a cool gift idea?

If you answered yes to the above, the VortexBoost electric shaker bottle is the smarter choice.

Smooth Texture

Smash you shakes into oblivion for a silky-smooth drink with no powder lumps or clumps. The built-in motor spins 6,000 times per minute to create a powerful vortex.

Mix Thick Shakes

Mixing thick shakes with a spoon is a recipe for disaster. With its powerful motor, this electric mixer cup can easily dissolve 5 scoops of protein shake powder in 14oz(450ml) of milk.

Powerful But Never Loud

The leak-free lid creates a sound barrier, so you can mix your beverages without disturbing people around you with loud noises. The vortex protein shaker is only about as quiet as typing on a keyboard.

Smoothie-like consistency all the time

With a powerful vortex that instantly blends even the thickest of protein powders, this advanced electric protein shaker bottle from VOLTRX puts the competition to shame. Simply add 14oz(450ml) of milk or water to your electric shaker cup and switch on your VortexBoost portable protein shake mixer. When the liquid has a deep 'tornado' in the center, toss in your favorite protein supplement and seal with the whisper quiet lid. Better still, VortexBoost electric shaker bottle feature customizable LED illumination that lights up the base when blending, giving you an eye-catching show of pulsating color. For silky smooth protein shakes every time, trust only VOLTRX.

As unique as you

Crafted To Last

VOLTRX protein shake mixer bottle are made of Tritan,100% BPA free. It looks and feels just like glass, but is lighter and significantly more durable.

Easy To Clean

Just fill it with water and gentle dishwashing soap, turn it on, and rinse it out. The base IPX7 waterproof, No need to remove the base. (The base is NOT dishwasher safe)

1 month of use from a 2-hour charge

The VOLTRX Electric Shaker Bottle's battery capacity ensures that a single charge can be used for a month (useful 3 times a week)

Complete kit

Product Weight: 1.3 lb
Package included:
1 x Juicer Blender
1 x Micro USB Charging Cable
1xBrush for Blender
1 x User Manual
When you get your Product, please pay attention to the following tips:
1.Don't put your hands inside your blender or try to touch the blades.
2.Don't use your blender when charging or run your blender without anything inside.
3.Don't recommend hot liquids over 50 degree which will be easy cause damage or leakage.
4.Charge your blender before your first use. The lights turns red while charging and blue once full charged.
5.Cut the fruits into 1.5*1.5CM or small thin pieces, remove the cores, hard thick fruit skin or hard shell.
6.Add water or milk and put appropriate amount of fruit slices into the juicer, turn over the juicer, press the switch button to make it work for a while, make the juicer back to the right position and shakes.
7.It is a normal phenomenon that juicer stop working. You can restart it. To get the best result, we advise you to shake the juicer during operating.
8.Red and blue flashing lights mean your jar isn't aligned with your base. To fix this, the arrow on the jar should line up with the switch on the base.
9.Red flashing lights mean your blender needs to be recharged or that your blades are blocked. Recharge or shake your blender.
10.There might be a little color difference due to the monitor, camera or other factors, please refer to the physical item.

name: Promixx Original Shaker Bottle (MiiXR Edition) - Battery-powered for Smooth Protein Shakes - BPA Free, 20oz Cup (White/Gray)
description:
PROMiXX Vortex Mixers Changed the Game

Effortless mixing at the touch of a button – PROMiXX Vortex Mixers mark an evolution from conventional shaker bottles. PROMiXX Vortex Mixers have been shown to provide superior mixing results to conventional shaker bottles. With industry-leading seals and impact and odor-resistant materials, the MiiXR AA is a blender bottle you can trust, without the mess. The Black/Gray design offers a premium, durable finish. The detachable motor unit allows for easy cleaning and, above all else, effortless mixing.

Detachable Motor, Easy to Clean

MiiXR AA has a detachable motor so it can be easily hand-washed. Add warm water and detergent, turn on, and let your new shaker bottle clean itself.

No shaking
No lumps
Better taste!

Durable & Leak-proof

The Shaker Bottle has Evolved!

MiiXR AA Powerful battery-operated Vortex Mixer for super-smooth protein shakes. Durable, BPA-free bottle with ultra-performance seals and leak-proof sports lid. It’s time to take a stand against lumpy protein shakes, rattling shaker cups and odor-retaining bottles!

As well as being stylish and ergonomic, MiiXR AA’s bottle is stain and odor resistant and easy-to-clean. Produced in tough durable AS copolymer, the bottle features a newly designed measuring scale, clearly indicating both ml + oz.

Twist-lock removable base unit
Double seal technology
Industry-leading seals
Splash proof

Go Above & Beyond

Super-Smooth Shakes On-the-Go

Athlete-tested for ergonomic design and portability, the AA is your perfect partner at home, in the gym, or on-the-go. Designed for convenience and quality, the MiiXR AA is perfect for those with a busy lifestyle. A vortex mixer that is portable, so that your supplements can be properly mixed with no mess for super-convenience.

Innovation Over Imitation

Designed in the UK, PROMiXX are the inventors of Vortex Mixing Technology and the global leading Vortex Mixer brand. Where others try to imitate, PROMiXX continues to innovate, educate and inspire. MiiXR AA will mix your protein shakes, preserving optimal micronutrient integrity using our patented Vortex Mixing Technology.

1 million+ Happy Customers

Global leaders in mixing technology, PROMiXX has sold over a million products. Endorsed by athletes worldwide - performance blending is in our DNA. They trust the PROMiXX patented X-Blade mixing technology to properly and effectively mix their supplements.

Q&A

What ingredients can I use with my Vortex Mixer?

Our mixers are intended for powdered nutrition/liquid ingredients. Get creative and try adding powdered peanut butter, pre-workout, flaxseed powder, cinnamon and much more. You could even use your shaker to mix your eggs or baby formula. NO solids.

What is included with my MiiXR AA?

Powerful detachable motor unit (requires 2 x AA batteries, NOT included); BPA/DEHP-free 600ml/20oz bottle; leak-proof sport-style lid; and user manual.

How do I mix with my MiiXR AA?

MIX. Add liquid ­– ideal fill = 9-14oz. Do NOT to use hot water. Push button to activate. Add powder into spinning vortex (do NOT add powder before activating vortex). Mix for 5-10 seconds. Deactivate vortex to preserve the battery. Enjoy!

How do I clean my Vortex Mixer? / Can I use a dishwasher to clean it?

HAND CLEAN ONLY. NOT dishwasher safe. Add warm water, a drop of detergent, and activate the vortex to self-clean. After, remove the motor unit and rinse the bottle with warm water. Do not get the motor unit wet. Do not use an abrasive sponge or scourer.

description: Start your journey to healthier living with the Hydrate Sport 24 ounce glass water bottle! features: 24OZ SHAKER CUP: Our refillable, reusable, 24oz capacity shaker cup is perfect for protein shakes, pre-workout drinks, iced coffee, or any beverage you want to take on the go!

TWO LID OPTIONS: Comes with 2 leak-proof lid options - the PRO lid features a flip-top cap and carry loop, while the Tumbler Lid With Straw is perfect for hot beverages and features a silicone rubber seal and smooth straw insertion.

MINDFUL DESIGN: Features double-walled insulation to eliminate sweat from outside of the cup, is shatterproof, and includes added isolation to regulate temperature - keeping your cold drinks cooler and warm drinks warmer. It is also cup-holder compatible with a silicone base and BPA free.
SMOOTH BLENDING: The included grate allows for easy, smooth mixing of supplement powders and can also be used to hold down ice and fruit for infused drinks.

CARE INSTRUCTIONS: Wash before first use. The dual function spout is dishwasher safe, however the glass bottle is hand wash only. Soak overnight or use a soft sponge or brush to clean tough stains. Rinse well after each wash.

description:
About this item

GLOW IN THE DARK SHAKER CUP: This one goes out to all the nocturnal folks out there who may also have a fear of the dark, have trouble finding things in the dark, or are simply fans of things which glow in the dark. Introducing, the Glow-In-The-Dark G Fuel Shaker Bottle. It’s lit! Literally.

SAFE, BPA FREE PLASTIC: Made from high-quality, BPA-free plastic, G Fuel Shaker Bottles are safe and built to withstand daily use.

name: Portable Blender for Shakes and Smoothies, OBERLY Personal Travel Blender for Protein with 4000mAh USB Rechargeable Battery, Crush Ice, Frozen Fruit and Drinks, 18 oz Mini Travel Cup
description:
Why Choose OBERLY Portable Blender?

OBERLY portable blender is so easy to use. It came with the mixing container which is a little water bottle. You can just drink out of it instead of having to pour it into another cup and wash it. It can chop up ice easily and blends whatever is put in there into a perfect smoothie.

Use ice cubes in the tray provided but it was strong enough to break those small ice cubes. Also little measurements help you know how much to put or how much you are drinking.

Adopting waterproof technology, it can effectively prevent water from entering the base of the portable blender during cleaning and causing engine damage. The personal blender can clean itself, just add a drop of soap, a bit of water, press twice the switch to start automatic cleaning.

Wanna make a delicious smoothies on the go? OBERLY portable blender is exactly what you need.

Specification:

Output Power: 175W
Motor: DC 7.4V, 22000 rpm±15%
Blade Material: 304 Stainless Steel
Cup Capacity: 18oz
Cup Material: PCTG Food Grade (BPA free)

Enjoy Juice, Share Life

OBERLY portable blender equipped with a stereoscopic structure designed 6-point stainless steel blades, powerful enough to mix all kinds of ingredients or even crush ice and frozen fruit easily. Portable design and 18oz large capacity cup allows you to take fresh drinks with you wherever you go. Super convenient self-clean function, forget about dirty cups and just enjoy the drinks!

OBERLY Portable Blender:

Get a ton of nutrients with little time and effort.
Easy to crush ice, frozen fruit, leafy greens and more into smoothies.
Perfect for shakes and smoothies, protein shake, milkshake, juice, yogurt, dressings.
Equipped with USB rechargeable that no need worry plug in world-wide.
Ease-of-use when it comes to travel, lifestyle needs, and its small size.
Convenience on the go.

Powerful Blending

The portable blender has six stainless steel blades and high rotation speed. They combine together and make the blender much powerful than others. The taste of the juice, smoothies or shakes will be much better.

Simple and Safe to Use

Single-button operation makes this personal blender quick and easy to use. Double click the switch to start working and it will prevent misoperation. LED indicators display working status.

4000mAh Battery

Built-in 4000mAh rechargeable battery, single charge for 3-5 hours provide more than 15 times continuous use. Save a lot of time for charging. You can make delicious juice for you and your family.

Safe and Humanized Design

Equipped with auto magnetic induction, the blender can work normally only when the two magnetic poles of the jar and the base are attached. Built-in safety features prevent overheating and overcharging, extending the life of it.

Portable and USB Rechargeable

Come with type-c port, built-in USB rechargeable can be easily charged by an USB charging, laptop charging, car charging and power bank with USB port or any other USB sources.

Waterproof Design and Easy to Clean

Adopting waterproof technology, it can effectively prevent water from entering the base of the portable blender during cleaning and causing engine damage. The personal blender can clean itself, just add a drop of soap, a bit of water, press twice the switch to start automatic cleaning.

Smoothies make the day go smoothly

Smoothies are refreshing, delicious, full of energy and make for a great start to the day. But smoothies take time in the morning. If you only give yourself time to get ready and leave for work, you will miss the breakfast.

Now you will never miss breakfast anymore with OBERLY portable smoothie blender. As long as you are to work on time in the morning, you can still make your breakfast and eat it right there, You can premeasure the fruits that you want to use and store those in the freezer at work, Use some banana, strawberry, ice, milk and whey powder and in less than a minute, you could hear it finished chopping up the ice, and you have a perfect smoothie.
